data.description: THIS IS THE ONE! 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bathroom home on sought-after Koestner street! You'll fall in love with the classic style of this beautiful 2-Story built in 1996. Home features a gas fireplace, formal dining area, ample sized bedrooms, partially finished basement, 2 car attached garage, fully enclosed vinyl privacy fence, huge yard, and much much more! DON"T MISS OUT! Call today to schedule a showing!
